social_posts.post_text: Happy Birthday to my #1 fan since I could remember. Your support has changed my life. I remember calling you about the idea of @happyice! It’s was your belief that pushed me to take the next steps to make it happen. Thank you for everything mom. We made it through so many storms together. From nothing to something. I’ll continue striving to make you proud and I’m excited to grow @collegeboycheesesteaks with you. You already know we repping #CBKFOREVER until we meet Kevin again. Happy Birthday mom @diamonddiva_ 💜💜
Show me your circle & I’ll tell you your future! #blackexcellence
GOD, Peace, Love & Happiness! #2023

Behind the scenes of our @happyice x @tmobile commercial😁 One day before production I began having health issues. T-mobile asked “is there anyone who could fill in for you”? Easiest question I’ve ever been asked. 

My fiancé @danielleemani . She put in the work with me to make @happyice what it is today. So she took off her Supermom cape and put on her @happyice cape and saved the day. Everyone help me thank her😁 #HappyIce #HappyFamily #Tmobile 

Ps. As you can see I couldn’t resist stopping by 😁

Los Angeles we’re searching for 4 great line cooks. A lot of big announcements coming and we’re excited to start growing our team. Let’s make history together. @collegeboycheesesteaks 

Send this any of your line cook friends in Los Angeles. We look forward to meeting some amazing people tomorrow and Tuesday. 

Starting pay: $19+ hour depending on experience.

@disneyland is highlighting @collegeboycheesesteaks for Black History month🔥 Let’s Gooooooo❗️We’re about to introduce Disney to real Philly Cheesesteaks. Man I love my city. It’s an honor to continue partnerships with my favorite brand in the world. 

Our mission continues with introducing the world to a Real Philly Cheesesteaks. Let’s kills it team. @collegeboymom @iammilanrouge @callmechefgeez

#CBKFOREVER ❗️We love you Kev @collegeboykev 🕊️

Had to bring in @collegeboykev Birthday with mom dukes at @collegeboycheesesteaks. I think it’s safe to say we’re keeping Kev name alive. 

Seeing you happy means the world to me. You’ve been on a mission and I know you gone reach your goals. Let’s continue to educate the world on our guy. Kevin White Jr aka College Boy Kev.  #CBKFOREVER 🕊️

Tribute to my brother Kevin that I made in 2015. 2 months after his passing. This was the point where I decided to turn my pain into my fuel. This is the point where I lost all fear and became a huge risk taker. I lived by the mindset “what’s the worse that can happen, I’m still alive”. 

I started believing that my brother lived through me and I wanted to show him the world. I haven’t let my foot off the gas yet. Keeping my brother name alive means everything to me. I’m so grateful for the time I had with him that I can’t even complain about wanting more. 

Kevin was so special. He made everyone feel loved. He always found time to check in on everyone, even a long lost cousin lol. He was the guy that always stopped pass your house if he was in the area. I hated this as a little brother in the passenger seat. Now I see the importance in what he did. My brother was really the best example I could of asked for. Thank you Kevin. 

 #CBKFOREVER and I mean it with my life. We gone take @collegeboycheesesteaks to the top in your name. 

Ps. For those who lost someone close to them I want to let you know GOD was the person that pulled me out of depression. I didn’t have the strength. I surrendered my life to him, he lift me up and has been using me since. 

All glory to GOD for pulling me out the darkness and making me a light.

Happy Birthday Kevin🕊️

Black Excellence! Been my favorite role model since I was a pup. Master at his craft, huge family man, built a school in his hometown and has replied to all the hate with more success. This the type of success I’m chasing down. 

Bron always makes his die heart fans proud. I sure can’t wait to have a comparison argument soon. I got a new clip of ammo!  #TeamBron 

What a time to be alive. We’ve witnessed history. @kingjames. Now I need you to come get a @happyice & @collegeboycheesesteaks to celebrate😁

@collegeboycheesesteaks x @disneyland today is the big day!  We’re a few hours away from being the first Philly Cheesesteak brand to vend in downtown @disneyland! It’s about to be a life changing experience for a lot of people today. 

Thank you everyone for your support to @collegeboycheesesteaks. Let’s continue to spread the word. 

Let’s go team @collegeboymom @callmechefgeez @iammilanrouge & #GOD! 

#CBKFOREVER

Fit👕: @milanodirouge

The juiciest and tastiest cheesesteak on the planet @collegeboycheesesteaks 🔥 I’m really addicted to these jawns. The best I’ve ever had and I’ve had it all. I promise I’m not just saying that because I’m the owner. Btw, my favorite is our bachelors with extra fried onions. Sometimes I add sweet peppers to mines too. Oh, saltpeppaketchup is a must🔥🧀🥩

Located in downtown @disneyland by the Star Wars trading post

Monday-Friday 3pm-Midnight 
Sat & Sun 12pm-Midnight
Did I f*ck it up or nah? That first spoon of @happyice a have you dancing😂 Blocking anyone who don’t say I killed it😂

Hello 31❗️How grateful I am for my family is all I could think about this birthday. I look at how far I’ve came and every step of the way I had someone to help me make it over the hurdles of life. Even if it was just them listening to my feelings. 

Birthdays are typically about the person who birthday it is, but I just want to thank GOD for the people he brung into my life. I love you all so much. 

Ps. Too many tags and photos to post of my friends and family. Y’all know who you are. Love y’all❗️Thank you. 

#CBKFOREVER

Getting robbed for cheesesteaks like they Jordan’s 😩 These Jawns from @collegeboycheesesteaks are way too good🔥 

Follow @collegeboycheesesteaks to see where the truck is popping up next. You can also subscribe on the website. 

📍7103 Sunset Blvd, Los Angeles CA 

S/O to the the team @iammilanrouge @collegeboymom @callmechefgeez. Drip by @milanodirouge.

I visit my brother accident site every time I’m in the city. I talk with him & I pray. A lot of the things I talked about here have came to fruition. 

The conversation I had with him this time is probably the most important one I’ve ever had. Excited to see what my future brings. The legacy continues. #CBKFOREVER 🕊️💜

I can’t explain the feeling but I want to feel this forever💜 

Thank you Jesus!

Happy Birthday to my sister from another mister! Anyone who gets to call you a friend, family, etc is lucky. You’re one of a kind. Ambitious, goofy, kind at heart but tough when necessary. The push and bully at the right times. You also listen to me and remain a student. It’s rare to have someone push me to be better. You don’t allow no excuses in your presence. If “if there’s a will there’s a way” was a person, it be you. Glad Jesus made us business partner and family. We gone make @collegeboycheesesteaks a household name. I honestly pray you are granted peace & happiness forever. You deserve it! Happy Birthday 🎂🥳

@iammilanrouge #Milano #TheBiggest
Y’all been asking & time has come. Black Ink LA💣 Next Monday May 15th.

“Blessed & Highly Favored” is my only answer for “How Are You”? 

Amazing night with an amazing team. It always feel like high school fun when I’m with the gang. #BlackInkLosAngeles

@happyice & @disneyland are back at it again🙏🏽🔥 Grateful is an understatement. Them inviting us inside last year was special. For them to invite us back again really means something. Who knows what this partnership might turn into. The team is going to execute day by day and let GOD handle the rest. 

Help me spread the word everyone. @happyice at the happiest place in the world. 🌈🍧

Ps. They really posted my @happyice cup with my logo clear as day. I know this small but it meant something to me. That let me know they really trust our brand. 

#HappyIce x #Disneyland

Thank you @missdiddy for bringing this all together. Thank you @themarathonclothing & @puma for green lighting her idea. 

They really wrapped the Happy Ice truck with marathon print! Now that’s hard🔥 This gave me a boost. 

The Marathon Continues 🏁

Some days I’m happy about the father I am and some days I’m sad about it. Some days I feel the mission I’m on for my kids means everything and sometimes it feels worthless. But every time I walk in the house, Summer and Sage make me feel like the best father in the world. I be needing those moments badly sometimes. Thank you Jesus for giving me the best kids I could ever ask for. Happy Father’s Day to all the fathers fighting to become a better father everyday. I’m fighting with you.
Pizza date with my princesses💜

That Philly hustle is different. It’s advised to never bet against us❗️

 @iammilanrouge @neodaviso #WestPhilly

Came out of retirement for a weekend and WON AN AWARD🙀🔥The half sleeve was only 60% done. Me winning was cool but having almost every artist at @enigmabeverlyhills win as well was unreal. Felt like we just won the NBA championship. Ready to run this back again. 

PS. Peep how happy everyone was when I won. Surround yourself with that type of energy. It’s different! 

#CBKFOREVER

My baby turned 4💜 My emotions have been all over the place. Nothing has made me happier then watching her grow. She’s insanely smart, such a leader, amazing big sister and a overall caring person. Daddy will strive to make you as proud of me as I am of you. #SummerMitchell #TheMitchells ✨

My goals have grown. I’m manifesting a BILLION❗️

Attending @ey_us was insanely motivating. I listened to the story of so many founders that have built multi-billion dollar brands. Attended workshops on how to build a billion dollar brand and connected with the best in the world. 

Congrats to my sis @iammilanrouge for making the Winning Women 2023 list. Also congrats on year 11 for @milanodirouge. Thank you for making sure I’m in these rooms. We got work to do💪🏾

@milanodirouge @happyice @collegeboycheesesteaks

Mandatory watch for the culture! Wow! Wow! Wow! Thank you @tylerperry. Thank you! 

I really needed this.

Happy Birthday Mom💜 You will go down in the “Ride or Die” hall of fame. No matter where I’m at in my journey of life, I know you got my back. Let’s continue to put on for Kev. #CBKFOREVER 

@diamonddiva_ 💜

Sending out prayers to everyone who has lost a sibling or a loved one they were very close to. This pain is unbearable at times. A never healing wound. 

Jesus please give me and those like me the strength to make it through the quiet & lonely times. Thats when the pain sneaks up on us and tries to takeover. Wrap your arms around your children in these moments. You’ve always shown up right on time and I know you will continue to do so. As always in these times, I ask for one thing. Please give me & those experiencing the same as me a dream with their loved one that feels so real. Make the laughs feel so real, the walks feel so real, the hugs feel so real, the quality time feel so real that we wake up in tears of joy. You always deliver on this requests when I ask but I’m requesting for others as well. I Love You, Thank You, Amen🙏🏽

Kevin White Jr.
2/4/89 - 4/29/15
#CBKFOREVER 

Your Little Brother Forever!
